<p>
	Bevvy is a platform for nightlife marketing. We work with leading nightlife venues and beverage brands to market discount offers to their customers via email, web, social media and mobile platforms.</p>
<p>
	We are seeking candidates to join our nightlife team and help expand our partnerships with bars and nightclubs in Los Angeles.</p>
<p>
	<strong><u>Sales Manager (Part-Time &amp; Full-Time positions)</u></strong></p>
<p>
	This is a great opportunity for someone looking to get their foot in the door with a dynamic new company.&nbsp;This opportunity offers significant growth potential with a fun, dynamic work environment.&nbsp;</p>
<p>
	Candidates will be responsible for negotiating deals and events with bar owners that will ultimately drive traffic to their venue.&nbsp;</p>
<p>
	<strong>Essential Qualities:</strong></p>
<p>
	Excitement about the startup environment and the possibility for high growth<br />
	Preference for a fast-paced, results-oriented environment.<br />
	Highly motivated with the ability to close business.<br />
	Outgoing personality and ability to build relationships quickly with decision makers.</p>
<p>
	<strong>Primary Responsibilities:</strong></p>
<p>
	Sales calls and meetings directly with vendors.<br />
	Structure and manage deal negotiations to successful closure and timely delivery.</p>
<p>
	<strong>Experience/Education/Skills Required:</strong></p>
<p>
	2+ years proven experience in B2B sales environment.<br />
	Outgoing personality, well spoken and entrepreneurial.<br />
	Self directed and self motivated.<br />
	Nightlife experience and contacts preferred.</p>
<p>
	To apply, email a resume and cover letter to tell us more about yourself.</p>
